Package: linkrvis
Type: Package
Title: Visualise Output from Genetic Linkage Analysis Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Peter", "Diakumis", email = "peterdiakumis@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Generates interactive plots for the visualisation of output
    from linkage analysis software, such as MERLIN, FEstim and PLINK.
License: MIT
LazyData: TRUE
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.1)
